title: 'Boys and Girl - Week 11 Lions Recap; Playoff Push; Pass First Identity with Cowboys.com's Dave Helman
itunes:title: 'Boys and Girl - Week 11 Lions Recap; Playoff Push; Pass First Identity with Cowboys.com's Dave Helman
description:
On today’s episode of the 'Boys and Girl Podcast, Jane and Bobby welcome David Helman from DallasCowboys.com to break down the big victory over the Lions, look ahead to the remainder of the season, and discuss the team’s new identity as a pass-first offense. Follow Jane and Bobby on Twitter and subscribe to get all the latest inside information from two of the most connected people in the Cowboys' community.
